## Architecture
- Use feature-first folder structure
- State management: Riverpod
- Common widgets go in lib/widgets/
- Theme files go in lib/theme/

## UI Rules
- Prefer Material 3
- Reuse theme colors and text styles first
- Break complex sections into reusable widgets
- Use const constructors where possible

## Assets
- Images: assets/images/
- SVG: assets/svg/
- Update pubspec.yaml when adding assets

## Figma Rules
- When using Figma MCP, prioritize semantic widget mapping
- Extract theme tokens before building full screens
- Prefer reusable components over one large page file
